OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781183479
OL,3,CMacclesfield FC co-owner to remain at
OL,4,Cclub following arrest
OL,6,FMacclesfield FC have confirmed its co-
OL,7,Fowner will remain on the board of
OL,8,Fdirectors following his arrest on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of controlling and coercive
OL,10,Fbehaviour.
OL,12,FRobert Smethurst, 48, was temporarily
OL,13,Frelieved of his duties after being
OL,14,Fdetained in May, but bosses say he has
OL,15,Fbeen reinstated and will "continue to
OL,16,Fsupport the football club's ongoing
OL,17,Fdevelopment".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
