FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781183479
OL,3,CMacclesfield FC co-owner to remain at
OL,4,Cclub following arrest
OL,6,FIn a statement on 10 June, the club's
OL,7,Fboard announced an agreed way forward
OL,8,Fhad been reached in the "best
OL,9,Finterests of the football club".
OL,11,FIt said: "Robert has acknowledged that
OL,12,Fsome of his recent comments and
OL,13,Factions have given rise to
OL,14,Funderstandable concern amongst
OL,15,Fsupporters.
OL,17,F"That recognition has formed an
OL,18,Fimportant part of the discussions
OL,19,Fwhich have taken place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781183479
OL,3,CMacclesfield FC co-owner to remain at
OL,4,Cclub following arrest
OL,6,F"The Board also notes that a number of
OL,7,Fcompletely unfounded claims regarding
OL,8,Fthe private lives of Board members
OL,9,Fhave circulated online during this
OL,10,Fperiod.
OL,12,F"We would like to make it absolutely
OL,13,Fclear that there is no basis
OL,14,Fwhatsoever for these allegations and
OL,15,Fwould urge supporters not to engage
OL,16,Fwith or perpetuate them.
OL,18,F"Throughout this period, the Board's
OL,19,Fpriority has remained the protection
OL,20,Fand long-term success of the Football
OL,21,FClub.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781183479
OL,3,CMacclesfield FC co-owner to remain at
OL,4,Cclub following arrest
OL,6,F"Robert has played a major role in
OL,7,Fhelping rebuild football in
OL,8,FMacclesfield and in establishing the
OL,9,Ffoundations that exist today."
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe club concluded its statement by
OL,17,Fsaying its focus was "firmly on the
OL,18,Ffuture and on ensuring that
OL,19,FMacclesfield FC continues to move
OL,20,Fforward as a Club that the whole
OL,21,Fcommunity can be proud of".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
