FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781183479
OL,3,CMacclesfield FC co-owner to remain at
OL,4,Cclub following arrest
OL,6,FIn an earlier statement, Cheshire
OL,7,FConstabulary confirmed a 48-year-old
OL,8,Fman was arrested in Wilmslow,
OL,9,FCheshire, on 19 May, and has been
OL,10,Fbailed pending further enquiries.
OL,12,FRobert Smethurst has denied the
OL,13,Fallegations on social media.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
